5.3 DUIM-Sheets Module

clipboard-owner

Generic function

Summary

Returns the sheet that owns the current clipboard data.

Signature

clipboard-owner clipboard => owner

Arguments

clipboard
An instance of <clipboard>.

Values

owner
An instance of <sheet>.

Library

duim-sheets

Module

duim-sheets

Description

Returns the sheet that owns the current clipboard data.

See also

<clipboard>, page 235
